<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>
<simplesect><title>template&lt;typename Event&gt;
class Util::Observer&lt; Event &gt;</title></simplesect>


<para>Abstract class template for observer in the observer design pattern. </para>



<para>An <link linkend="_classUtil_1_1Observer">Observer</link> is notified of an event by calling its update method. The template class parameter Event is the type of object that is passed to the <link linkend="_classUtil_1_1Observer_1a518cb0d0b98052c436d4a52c61edc80b">update()</link> method as a message about an event. </para>
